text: always come for a sashimi here since its affordable. Yesterday, i ordered a sashimi as well as a crab-stick sushi. Don't know if it was the crab stick or the sashimi but i got a food poisoning from it. (it was the only meal i ate yesterday). very disappointed and not be ordering those again.

First time trying a sushi takeaway.

Price played a huge factor -$6.90 for this salmon chirashi bowl/don.  It was pretty nice.

Price comparison :
Pao Pao fan -$6.50
Qiqi mee rebus $4+ (no meat)
Qiqi mee rebus special $5+??
Food court fried chicken and rice $5-6+

So it was like no brainer for $6.90 for Japanese cuisine.
service is good, sushi is fresh.
Affordable express sushi takeout. Taste wise pretty standard. Can't complain for the price.
The sushi were delicious and thank god it's affordable!!!
